ribals%20form%2032%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20population.%20They%20are%20the%20largest%20population%20group%20in%20the%20state%20after%20the%20Other%20Backward%20Classes%20--%20a%20situation%20that%20had%20initially%20left%20the%20BJP%20torn%20between%20picking%20a%20tribal%20and%20an%20OBC%20member.%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%2C%20however%2C%20went%20in%20favour%20of%20tribals%20in%20view%20of%20the%20party's%20unprecedented%20performance%20in%20the%20states'%20tribal%20areas.%20The%20BJP%2C%20never%20on%20top%20of%20tribals'%20list%20of%20favourites%2C%20had%20managed%20to%20turn%20around%20the%20mood%20and%20corner%20all%2014%20assembly%20seats%20in%20the%20tribal-dominated%20Surguja%20region%20and%20eight%20of%20the%2012%20seats%20in%20Bastar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sai%2C%2059%2C%20is%20also%20known%20to%20be%20favoured%20by%20the%20party's%20ideological%20mentor%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh.%20Additionally%2C%20he%20is%20close%20to%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Raman%20Singh%2C%20who%20has%20been%20the%20party's%20tallest%20leader%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20four-term%20MP%20--%20who%20has%20been%20the%20president%20of%20the%20Chhattisgarh%20unit%20of%20the%20party%20from%202020%20to%202022%20--%20is%20known%20for%20his%20organisational%20capability%20and%20has%20a%20non-controversial%20image.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%2C%20he%20has%20been%20a%20member%20of%20the%20BJP%20National%20Working%20Committee.%20When%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20came%20to%20power%20in%202014%2C%20he%20was%20named%20as%20the%20junior%20minister%20for%20steel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThanking%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20BJP%20president%20J%20P%20Nadda%20and%20other%20party%20leaders%2C%20Mt%20Sai%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20Chief%20Minister%2C%20I%20will%20try%20to%20fulfil%20PM%20Modi's%20guarantees%20through%20the%20government%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESanctioning%2018%20lakh%20houses%20(to%20beneficiaries%20of%20a%20housing%20scheme)%20will%20be%20the%20first%20work%20(to%20be%20done)%20in%20the%20state%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20Mr%20Sai%20could%20be%20picked%20for%20a%20larger%20role%20was%20indicated%20by%20Union%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20who%20while%20addressing%20a%20poll%20rally%20in%20the%20Kunkuri%20last%20month%2C%20had%20asked%20the%20voters%20to%20elect%20him.%20Mr%20Sai%20would%20be%20made%20a%20%26quot%3Bbig%20man%26quot%3B%20if%20the%20party%20comes%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%2C%20Mr%20Shah%20had%20said%2C%20.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20won%2054%20seats%20in%20the%2090-member%20Assembly%20in%20the%20recently%20held%20assembly%20election%20and%20wrested%20power%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20which%20was%20reduced%20to%2035%20seats%20from%20the%2068%20it%20won%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702208460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fi7uv7u8o_vishnu-sai-1200-_625x300_10_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-union-minister-vishnu-deo-sai-is-the-new-chhattisgarh-chief-minister-sources-4651040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chhattisgarh%20New%20Chief%20Minister%3A%20Vishnu%20Deo%20Sai%20%2C%20tribal%20leader%20and%20former%20Union%20Minister%20is%20the%20BJP's%20pick%20as%20the%20next%20Chief%20Minister%20of%20Chhattisgarh%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%202024%20general%20election.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-union-minister-vishnu-deo-sai-is-the-new-chhattisgarh-chief-minister-sources-4651040%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-union-minister-vishnu-deo-sai-is-the-new-chhattisgarh-chief-minister-sources-4651040%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fformer-union-minister-vishnu-deo-sai-is-the-new-