variety.com%2F2023%2Ftv%2Fnews%2Fiqiyi-2024-tv-production-taiwan-thailand-malaysia-1235832346%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22My%20best%20friend%20is%2029%20years%20older%20than%20I%20am%20and%20we've%20never%20met%20in%20person.%20Age%20is%20irrelevant%20to%20us.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20over%20the%20shoulder%20of%20person%20texting%20on%20phone%20screen.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6570e9a67a3c8094d5da6f4e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221414%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAuthor%20not%20pictured.%3Cp%3ECavan%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20I%20made%20a%20business%20decision%20that%20didn't%20work%20out%2C%20I%20posted%20a%20video%20about%20it%20on%20my%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20video%20resonated%20with%20a%20woman%20named%20Cyd.%20She%20reached%20out%20to%20me%20over%20email.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESince%20then%2C%20she's%20become%20one%20of%20my%20best%20friends%2C%20even%20though%20we're%20almost%2030%20years%20apart.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20opened%20my%20inbox%20in%20early%20December%202019%2C%20I%20never%20expected%20to%20meet%20a%20woman%20who%20would%20become%20one%20of%20my%20best%20friends%20%E2%80%94%20despite%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffriend-decades-older-reminds-me-age-privilege-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E30%20years%20my%20senior%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'd%20been%20trying%20to%20grow%20my%20business%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvegan-diet-better-for-health-than-omnivore-identical-twins-study-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant-based%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20coach%20while%20paying%20the%20bills%20with%20my%20writing.%20When%20a%20podcast%20I'd%20been%20following%20touted%20online%20wellness%20programs%20as%20the%20answer%2C%20I%20jumped%20on%20the%20idea%20%E2%80%94%20and%20it%20failed%20spectacularly.%20I%20fell%20into%20a%20funk%20as%20I%20tried%20to%20work%20out%20what%20had%20gone%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20realized%20my%20biggest%20problem%20was%20forgetting%20I'd%20become%20a%20health%20coach%20to%20help%20people%2C%20not%20get%20rich%20quick.%20I%20posted%20a%20video%20apologizing%20to%20my%20audience%20for%20being%20something%20I%20wasn't.%20Then%2C%20out%20of%20the%20blue%2C%20I%20got%20an%20email%20that%20changed%20my%20mood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20email%20was%20from%20a%20fellow%20nutrition%20educator%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20named%20Cyd%20Notter%20had%20found%20my%20website%20after%20reading%20an%20article%20I'd%20written%20for%20a%20plant-based%20nonprofit%20organization.%20She%20emailed%20me%20to%20say%20she%20was%20facing%20struggles%20similar%20to%20those%20I%20shared%20in%20the%20video%3A%20feeling%20caught%20up%20in%20promotional%20activities%20that%20didn't%20fulfill%20the%20intended%20purpose%20of%20her%20own%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20shared%20concerns%20stemmed%20from%20a%20mutual%20foundation%20in%20the%20Christian%20faith.%20We%20both%20wanted%20to%20honor%20God%20in%20our%20businesses%20and%20were%20at%20a%20crossroads%20as%20we%20prayed%20through%20what%20that%20should%20look%20like.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20was%20a%20big%20deal%20for%20me.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20didn't%20have%20any%20close%20friends%20who%20were%20Christians%20or%20who%20followed%20a%20fully%20plant-based%20lifestyle.%20(In%20fact%2C%20later%2C%20I%20learned%20that%20Cyd%20literally%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcydnotter.com%2Fplan-a-whole-foods-no-oil-plant-based-diet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cu%3Ewrote%20the%20book%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20connection%20between%20plant-based%20eating%20and%20faith!)%20The%20unique%20combination%20of%20our%20interests%20established%20a%20strong%20connection%20between%20us%20from%20the%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20quickly%20learned%20that%20we%20were%20similar%20in%20many%20other%20ways.%20For%20example%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20use%20what%20we%20learned%20from%20our%20health%20coach%20training%20to%20help%20others%20improve%20their%20well-being.%20And%20we%20both%20loved%20cooking%20tasty%20plant-based%20recipes!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20friendship%20has%20only%20grown%20stronger%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20though%20we've%20still%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fcouple-dated-for-a-year-before-meeting-in-person-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enever%20met%20in%20person%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Cyd%20and%20I%20talk%20on%20the%20phone%20several%20times%20a%20year%20%E2%80%94%20sometimes%20for%20over%20an%20hour.%20We%20catch%20up%20on%20life%2C%20business%2C%20and%20spiritual%20matters%20as%20if%20we've%20known%20each%20other%20forever.%20But%20whereas%20some%20of%20my%20relationships%20with%20older%20friends%20have%20felt%20like%20relating%20to%20a%20parent%20or%20an%20aunt%2C%20Cyd%20is%20like%20an%20older%20sister%20with%20whom%20I%20can%20be%20open%20about%20what's%20going%20on%20in%20my%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20appreciate%20that%20she%20understands%20what%20I%20mean%20when%20I%20share%20the%20struggles%20and%20triumphs%20of%20my%20Christian%20walk%20and%20how%20I%20feel%20God%20is%20leading%20me.%20And%20I%20know%20she's%20always%20up%20for%20lighter%20conversation%2C%20like%20exchanging%20our%20plant-based%20recipes!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20pray%20for%20each%20other%20at%20the%20end%20of%20our%20talks%2C%20and%20I%20come%20away%20feeling%20uplifted%2C%20refreshed%2C%20and%20encouraged.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20rarely%20talk%20about%20age%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20met%20over%20email%2C%20I%20knew%20Cyd%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffell-in-love-with-best-friend-came-out-lesbian-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eolder%20than%20me%3C%2Fa%3E%2C