n%20expect%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhat's%20being%20proposed%20for%20student-debt%20relief%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EA%20week%20before%20the%20final%20negotiation%20session%2C%20the%20Education%20Department%20released%20an%20updated%20draft%20text%20for%20the%20final%20relief%20plan.%20It%20highlighted%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-who-will-qualify-second-attempt-biden-education-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20groups%20of%20borrowers%20it's%20planning%20to%20target%20for%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20on%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20with%20balances%20greater%20than%20what%20they%20originally%20borrowed%2C%20eligible%20for%20up%20to%20%2420%2C000%20in%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20borrowers%20with%20balances%20greater%20than%20what%20they%20originally%20borrowed%2C%20eligible%20for%20up%20to%20%2410%2C000%20in%20relief.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20whose%20loans%20entered%20repayment%20at%20least%2020%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20eligible%20for%20relief%20under%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20or%20other%20targeted%20programs%20like%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20but%20have%20not%20applied.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3EBorrowers%20who%20went%20to%20schools%20that%20left%20them%20with%20too%20much%20debt%20compared%20to%20their%20post-grad%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20December%20session%2C%20negotiators%20will%20discuss%20those%20proposed%20groups%2C%20along%20with%20alternate%20ways%20to%20get%20relief%20to%20another%20group%20of%20borrowers%20experiencing%20hardship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20proposed%20text%20also%20includes%20language%20likely%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwill-biden-new-student-loan-forgiveness-plan-face-lawsuits-relief-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blan