take%20away%20the%20impact%20player%20rule%3A%20Jaffer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702205563000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105878972%2Cimgsize-32942.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fipl%2Ftop-stories%2Fipl-needs-to-take-away-the-impact-player-rule-feels-wasim-jaffer%2Farticleshow%2F105878994.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Indian%20cricketer%20Wasim%20Jaffer%20took%20to%20social%20media%20platform%20'X'%2C%20formerly%20Twitter%2C%20to%20articulate%20his%20apprehensions%20about%20the%20adverse%20impact%20of%20the%20'Impact%20Player'%20rule%20on%20the%20bowling%20skills%20and%20overall%20progress%20of%20all-rounders.%20According%20to%20the%20'Impact%20Player'%20rule%2C%20a%20franchise%20has%20the%20flexibility%20to%20substitute%20a%20player%20from%20the%20playing%20eleven%20with%20one%20of%20the%20five%20substitutes%20named%20during%20the%20toss%2C%20providing%20teams%20with%20added%20depth%20in%20either%20batting%20or%20bowling%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20match.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20did%20a%20voluntary%20work%20exchange%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20and%20lived%20one%20month%20for%20free.%20The%20experience%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20my%20truest%20self.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dena%20Levitz%20taking%20a%20selfie%20with%20the%20lush%20green%20Costa%20Rican%20forest%20behind%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657366847a3c8094d5db2fa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Arenal%20Volcano%2C%20in%20the%20distance%2C%20was%20a%20short%20walk%20from%20the%20ranch%20where%20Dena%20Levitz%20lived%20free%20for%20one%20month%20during%20her%20voluntary%20work%20exchange.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dena%20Levitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDena%20Levitz%20lived%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20for%20one%20month%20on%20a%20voluntary%20work%20exchange.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%C2%A0She%20found%20the%20program%20through%20a%20website%20that%20connects%20yoga%20instructors%20with%20resorts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELevitz%20said%20the%20experience%20changed%20her%20approach%20to%20traveling%20and%20living%20sustainably.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20tail%20end%20of%202019%2C%20I%20moved%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthings-to-do-in-dublin-ireland%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDublin%2C%20Ireland%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20where%20I'd%20spent%20the%20prior%20four%20years%20on%20a%20work%20visa%20%E2%80%94%20back%20to%20the%20US%20to%20make%20a%20new%20life%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELiving%20in%20a%20major%20urban%20center%20with%20skyscrapers%2C%20subways%2C%20and%20endless%20entertainment%20was%20a%20goal%20of%20mine%20for%20years%2C%20but%20after%20a%20mere%20three%20months%20enjoying%20and%20settling%20into%20NYC%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fphotos-coroanvirus-lockdown-changed-times-square-2020-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECOVID%20pandemic%20abruptly%20shut%20everything%20down%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20a%20seasoned%20traveler%2C%20who'd%20visited%2035%20countries%2C%20staying%20put%20ran%20counter%20to%20all%20of%20my%20impulses%2C%20and%20I%20leaned%20into%20my%20yoga%20practice%20and%20teaching%20for%20needed%20solace%20and%20comfort.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20COVID%20became%20less%20of%20a%20threat%2C%20I%20decided%20I%20needed%20to%20get%20back%20out%20in%20the%20world%20and%2C%20perhaps%2C%20I%20could%20do%20it%20differently%20this%20time.%20I%20started%20brainstorming%20out-of-the-box%2C%20cheap%20travel%20hacks%20earlier%20this%20year%20with%20a%20friend%20and%20ended%20up%20swapping%20yoga%20instructions%20for%20a%20free%20month%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fmoved-from-colorado-to-costa-rica-blue-zone-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Costa%20Rica%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20courtesy%20of%20a%20work%20exchange%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20experience%20reinvigorated%20me%20and%20has%20changed%20my%20approach%20to%20traveling%20and%20living%20sustainably%20ever%20since.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20came%20across%20a%20website%20that%20listed%20retreats%20offering%20free%20stay%20to%20yoga%20instructors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20website%20is%20set%20up%20like%20a%20dating%20platform.%20Yoga%20teachers%20create%20profiles%20to%20tout%20their%20training%20and%20experience%2C%20while%20retreat%20centers%2C%20studios%2C%20and%20resorts%20post%20openings%20for%20instructors%20to%20come%20lead%20mindful%20movement%20classes%20or%20special%20events%20onsite.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20what%20I%20could%20gather%2C%20the%20frequent%20setup%20was%20that%20teachers%20were%20compensated%20not%20so%20much%20with%20money%2C%20but%20with%20free%20lodging%2C%20meals%2C%20and%20other%20perks.%20Right%20away%2C%20a%20sustainable%20ranch%20in%20a%20remote%20rainforest-laden%20part%20of%20Costa%20Rica%20stuck%20out%20to%20me.%20It%20was%20close%20to%20Lake%20Arenal%20and%20the%20Arenal%20Volcano%2C%20and%20I%20appreciated%20that%2C%20while%20guests%20came%20from%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20its%2050-person%20staff%20was%20primarily%20Costa%20Rican.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20ranch%20required%20a%20one-month%20commitment%20for%20a%20%3Cstrong%3Evoluntary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Ework%20exchange%20gig%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20a%20yoga%20center%20per%20se%3B%20more%20of%20a%20carbon-negative%20community.%20The%20eco-resort%20sat%20on%20400-acres%20and%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fyoga-classes-solo-travel-mindfulness-culture-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebeautiful%20outdoor%20yoga%20%3C%2Fa%3Eshala%2C%20natural%20swimming%20pools%2C%20an%20extensive%20garden%2C%20and%20a%20farm%20with%20chickens%20and%20pigs%2C%20and%20horses%20who%20ran%20free%20when%20not%20being%20corralled%20for%20riding%20excursions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20exactly%20the%20kind%20of%20nature-focused%20setting%20I%20was%20so%20desperately%20craving%2C%20so%20I%20reached%20out.%20Getting%20%26quot%3Bhired%26quot%3B%20and%20setting%20arrangements%20took%20an%20application%3B%20reference%20checks%3B%20and%20an%20interview%20with%20the%20ranch%20owner's%20wife%2C%20a%20yogi%20herself.%20The%20application%20process%20took%20three%20months.%20By%20March%20we%20had%20agreed%20on%20my%20start%20date%2C%20July%2015%20with%20the%20option%20to%20extend%20my%20time%20if%20both%20sides%20desired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Pigs%20in%20a%20gate%20on%20the%20eco-farm.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6573a3da58e7c0c29a2b6331%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20eco-farm%20had%20chickens%2C%20pigs%2C%20and%20horses.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dena%20Levitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20each%20day%20I%20taught%20one%20or%20two%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Ftypes-of-yoga%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%2060-minute%20yoga%20classes%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Most%20days%20I%20also%20spent%20two%20or%20three%20hours%20assisting%20with%20basic%20physical%20tasks%20on%20%26quot%3BLa%20Huerta%26quot%3B%20(the%20vegetable%20garden)%20like%20pulling%20weeds.%20In%20exchange%2C%20the%20ranch%20provided%20me%20with%20a%20bed%20and%20three%20meals%20a%20day%2C%20cooked%20by%20a%20well-trained%20kitchen%20staff%20from%20food%20primarily%20grown%20on%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20stay%20was%20complimentary%2C%20but%20there%20were%20aspects%20I%20needed%20to%20cover%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20mainly%20needed%20to%20get%20myself%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20and%20to%20the%20sustainable%20ranch%20site%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20the%20price%20of%20flights%20vary.%20I%20booked%20a%20direct%20flight%20to%20San%20Jos%C3%A9%2C%20Costa%20Rica%2C%20from%20JFK%20in%20May%2C%20far%20enough%20in%20advance%20that%20the%20round-trip%20direct%20flights%20cost%20me%20under%20%24700.%20The%20ranch%20required%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fbest-travel-insurance-companies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproof%20of%20travel%20insurance%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20sort-of%20guarantee%20that%20volunteers%20would%20show%20up.%20This%20I%20managed%20to%20purchase%20for%20about%20%24175%20overall.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22469%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dena%20Levitz%20in%20Costa%20Rica%20sitting%20on%20a%20rock%20where%20she%20meditated%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6573a27c0ec98e92f74dddbc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22352%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELevitz%20would%20often%20sit%20in%20nature%20and%20meditate%20during%20the%20work%20exchange.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dena%20Levitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20other%20travel%20cost%20was%20a%20shuttle%20from%20the%20airport%20in%20San%20Jos%C3%A9%20to%20the%20very%20remote%20ranch%20site%20about%20four%20hours%20away.%20Here%2C%20the%20volunteer%20coordinator%20suggested%20a%20local%20shuttle%20company%20that%20made%20the%20trek%20once%20a%20day%20for%20about%20%2465%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20home%20in%20New%20York%20I%20managed%20to%20find%20a%20friend%20of%20a%20friend%20who%20could%20stay%20in%20my%20apartment%2C%20care%20for%20my%20plants%2C%20and%20pay%20my%20living%20expenses%20while%20I%20was%20away%2C%20so%20I%20could%20afford%20the%20trip.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ENot%20being%20entirely%20free%20to%20enjoy%20down%20time%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20bummer%20that%20we%20poked%20fun%20at%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBecause%20I%20was%20essentially%20unpaid%20staff%2C%20there%20was%20a%20set%20routine%20and%20certain%20rules%20the%20team%20of%20volunteers%20had%20to%20abide%20by.%20We%20especially%20had%20to%20follow%20rules%20around%20when%20to%20access%20the%20buffet%20at%20meal%20times%20and%20which%20swimming%20areas%20were%20on%20and%20off%20limits%20(so%20guests%20got%20first%20priority).%20We%20learned%20to%20accept%20the%20schedule%2C%20given%20all%20of%20the%20positive%20aspects%20of%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20opposed%20to%20the%20more%20spacious%20bungalows%2C%20complete%20with%20hammocks%20and%20fans%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fvolunteer-sustainable-travel-wwoofing-organic-farm-in-switzerland-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ework%20exchange%20volunteers%3C%2Fa%3E%20stayed%20in%20the%20more%20dorm-like%20farmhouse.%20That%20setup%20lacked%20any%20internet%20access%20and%20featured%20communal%20showers%2C%20small%20individual%20rooms%20with%20twin-size%20bunk%20beds%2C%20and%20a%20steady%20slew%20of%20mosquitoes%20%3Cspan%3Ewhose%20preferred%20feast%20seemed%20to%20be%20my%20feet%3C%2Fspan%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20small%20room%20with%20bunk%20beds.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6573a30658e7c0c29a2b6304%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EVolunteers%20slept%20in%20a%20dorm-like%20farmhouse%20with%20bunkbeds.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dena%20Levitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20accommodations%20weren't%20exactly%20the%20high%20point.%20But%20it%20was%20the%20one%20aspect%20that%20pandemic%20life%20in%20a%20small%20Manhattan%20apartment%20had%20prepared%20me%20for.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EOf%20highest%20value%20to%20me%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20be%20part%20of%20a%20sustainable%20community%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20really%20got%20to%20know%20the%20inner%20workings%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbetter-me%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20sustainable%20community%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20the%20kind%20of%20place%20where%20nothing%20is%20wasted%20%E2%80%94%20animal%20excrement%20is%20composted%2C%20cooking%20oil%20becomes%20the%20basis%20for%20soap%2C%20and%20extra%20greens%20like%20kale%20are%20chopped%20up%20and%20fed%20to%20the%20fish%2C%20swimming%20in%20a%20pond%20adjacent%20to%20the%20farm.%20Seeing%20this%20level%20of%20environmental%20urgency%20in%20action%20was%20truly%20inspiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20daily%20yoga%20classes%20were%20predetermined%3A%20a%207%20a.m.%20more%20dynamic%20class%20and%20a%204%20p.m%20more%20restorative%20class.%20After%20a%20few%20days%20of%20adjusting%20to%20teaching%20over%20the%20vibrant%20sounds%20of%20the%20rushing%20river%2C%20chirping%20birds%2C%20and%20frequent%20rainstorms%2C%20my%20creativity%20as%20a%20yoga%20teacher%20soared.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dena%20Levitz%20doing%20a%20yoga%20pose%20at%20shala.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6573a36158e7c0c29a2b6311%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ELevitz%20taught%20two%20classes%20each%20day%20during%20the%20work%20exchange%20program.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dena%20Levitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wasn't%20bogged%20down%20with%20the%20kinds%20of%20peripheral%20thoughts%20that%20might%20distract%20me%20at%20home%3A%20%3Cem%3EHow%20would%20I%20get%20to%20that%20far-off%20Brooklyn%20studio%20where%20I'd%20be%20subbing%20today%3F%20Did%20I%20need%20to%20bring%20props%3F%20Was%20there%20a%20different%20invoicing%20system%20for%20this%20business%3F%20%3C%2Fem%3EAs%20I%20began%20to%20feel%20comfortable%20with%20the%20regular%20cadence%20of%20the%20day%2C%20I%20found%20myself%20clear-headed%2C%20more%20present%20and%20loving%20the%20ability%20to%20teach%20exactly%20who%20was%20in%20front%20of%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThis%20is%20how%20life%20should%20be%20lived%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20fair%20to%20say%20I%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Ffoods-to-eat-for-better-sleep-2017-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeating%20and%20sleeping%20better%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20day%20five%20I%20was%20waking%20up%20at%205%3A45%20a.m.%20without%20an%20alarm%20and%20sitting%20in%20meditation%20amidst%20the%20trees%20before%20doing%20anything%20else.%20In%20contrast%20to%20New%20York%2C%20where%20I%20was%20often%20awake%20well%20past%20midnight%2C%20evenings%20at%20the%20ranch%20usually%20wrapped%20before%2010%20p.m.%20with%20me%20practicing%20my%20Spanish%2C%20having%20sing-alongs%20with%20staff%2C%20and%20cozying%20up%20to%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Costa%20Rican%20forest%20near%20a%20retreat.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6573a4270ec98e92f74dde2f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22360%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%20Rows%20of%20herbs%20and%20vegetables%20in%20La%20Huerta%2C%20the%20vegetable%20garden%20on%20the%20eco-farm.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Dena%20Levitz%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20day%2C%20the%20work%20that%20I%20undertook%20in%20the%20garden%20felt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fmental-health%2Fmindfulness-meditation%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeditative%20and%20meaningful%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%2C%20through%20my%20individual%20efforts%2C%20I%20was%20tangibly%20contributing%20and%20creating.%20If%20I%20was%20harvesting%20jalape%C3%B1os%2C%20for%20example%2C%20the%20peppers%20would%20show%20up%20on%20the%20dinner%20spread%20later%2C%20and%20this%20made%20me%20proud.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeing%20connected%20to%20something%20bigger%20than%20myself%20was%20more%20satisfying%20than%20I%20could%20have%20imagined%20and%20something%20I'm%20constantly%20trying%20to%20recapture%20back%20in%20New%20York.%20This%20experience%20made%20me%20feel%20like%20my%20truest%20self.%20It's%20a%20reset%20I'd%20like%20to%20repeat%20each%20year%20going%20forward%20and%20would%20recommend%20to%20anyone%20else%20seeking%20a%20similar%20feeling%20of%20connection%20in%20a%20travel%20destination.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-do-voluntary-work-exchange-in-costa-rica-2023-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702205521000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657366847a3c8094d5db2fa1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-do-voluntary-work-exchange-in-costa-rica-2023-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20yoga%20instructor%20traveled%20to%20Costa%20Rica%20on%20a%20voluntary%20work%20exchange%20and%20shares%20her%20experience%20along%20with%20the%20cost%20and%20process.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Dena%20R.%20Levitz)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-do-voluntary-work-exchange-in-costa-rica-2023-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20New%20York%20hospital%20pushed%20weight%20loss%20surgeries%20on%20prisoners%20and%20left%20some%20malnourished%2C%20report%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Rikers%20Island%20jail%20complex%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20with%20the%20Manhattan%20skyline%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63bc692a23f36200198781f9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221598%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Rikers%20Island%20jail%20complex%20in%20New%20York%20City%2C%20with%20the%20Manhattan%20skyline%20in%20the%20background.%3Cp%3ESeth%20Wenig%2FAP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBellevue%20Hospital%20in%20New%20York%20performs%20thousands%20of%20bariatric%20surgeries%20a%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20NYT%20investigation%20found%20that%20it%20performed%20surgeries%20on%20some%20Rikers%20Island%20prisoners%20who%20then%20became%20malnourished.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETwo%20prisoners%20say%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20meet%20the%20post-surgery%20dietary%20requirements%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20public%20hospital%20in%20New%20York%20famed%20for%20its%20lucrative%20weight-loss%20surgeries%20also%20performed%20on%20prisoners%2C%20at%20least%20two%20of%20whom%20say%20they%20were%20left%20malnourished%2C%20a%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20New%20York%20Times%20investigation%20into%20Bellevue%20Hospital's%20procedures%20found%20that%20it%20had%20performed%20about%20a%20record%203%2C000%20weight-loss%20surgeries%20this%20year%2C%20sometimes%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2023%2F12%2F07%2Fbusiness%2Fbariatric-surgery-bellevue-hospital.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E%20rushing%20inappropriate%20patients%20through%20the%20process.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20included%20at%20least%2011%20prisoners%20from%20New%20York%20City's%20Rikers%20Island%20jail%20complex%20who%20underwent%20elective%20bariatric%20surgery%20at%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBariatric%20surgery%20is%20a%20major%20operation%20that%20shrinks%20a%20patient's%20stomach%20and%20requires%20them%20to%20change%20their%20eating%20habits%2C%20such%20as%20by%20eating%20small%2C%20protein-rich%20meals%20%E2%80%93%20a%20level%20of%20control%20over%20one's%20diet%20that%20is%20near%20impossible%20in%20prison.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20Rikers%20prisoner%2C%20David%20Mustiga%2C%20who%20weighed%20300%20pounds%2C%20said%20that%20he%20was%20told%20about%20the%20surgery%20without%20being%20warned%20of%20the%20di