m.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20does%20it%20matter%20which%20of%20the%20individual%20ministers%20in%20the%20same%20ministry%20signed%20an%20official%20answer%3F%20Is%20this%20the%20respect%20ministers%20have%20for%20their%20government%E2%80%99s%20views%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeenakshi%20Lekhi%20is%20a%20minister%20in%20the%20same%20government%20as%20the%20one%20that%20has%20answered%20the%20question%2C%20asking%20whether%20India%20believed%20that%20Hamas%20was%20a%20terrorist%20organisation.%20%E2%80%9CDesignation%20of%20an%20organisation%20as%20terrorist%20is%20covered%20under%20the%20Unlawful%20Activities%20Prevention%20Act%20(UAPA)%20and%20declaring%20any%20organisation%20as%20terrorist%20is%20considered%20as%20per%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Act%20by%20the%20relevant%20government%20departments%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20answer%20by%20the%20ministry%20of%20external%20affairs%20to%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20Unstarred%20Question%20No.%20980%2C%20on%20December%208%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELekhi%2C%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20External%20Affairs%20no%20less%2C%20distanced%20herself%20from%20the%20question.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20not%20signed%20any%20paper%20with%20this%20question%20and%20this%20answer%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%20in%20response%20to%20a%20post%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20error%E2%80%9D%20could%20have%20been%20sorted%20out%20quietly%20and%20internally.%20Did%20it%20require%20Lekhi%20holding%20a%20political%20press%20conference%20at%20the%20BJP%20headquarters%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20indeed%20a%20%E2%80%9Ctechnical%20error%E2%80%9D%20as%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20in%20its%20statement%20soon%20after%20Lekhi%20created%20a%20fuss%2C%20and%20held%20a%20political%20press%20conference%20against%20her%20own%20ministry%20and%20said%20there%20would%20be%20a%20hunt%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cculprit%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20press%20conference%20suggests%20dissonance%20and%20confusion.%20Do%20all%20ministers%20not%20hold%20the%20same%20view%20as%20the%20Union%20government%20does%3F%20This%20is%20a%20government%20that%20prescribes%20%E2%80%9Cone%E2%80%9D%20of%20everything.%20Surely%2C%20all%20ministers%20can%20be%20held%20to%20%E2%80%9Cone%E2%80%9D%20view%20on%20such%20an%20important%20matter%3F%20Is%20%3Cem%3Eek%20sarkar%2C%20ek%20jawaab%3C%2Fem%3E%20too%20much%20to%20expect%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20are%20decisions%20made%20in%20the%20Modi%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELekhi%20tagged%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20external%20affairs%20minister%20publicly%20on%20X.%20There%20was%20another%20tweet%20that%20asked%20about%20the%20official%20website%20of%20MEA%20uploading%20the%20question.%20The%20tweet%20questioned%20if%20Lekhi%20didn%E2%80%99t%20prepare%20the%20question%2C%20who%20did.%20Responding%20to%20this%20question%2C%20Lekhi%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAn%20inquiry%20will%20reveal%20the%20culprit.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20speaks%20poorly%20of%20internal%20discussion%20mechanisms%20within%20a%20government%20that%20should%20know%20better.%20Coalition%20governments%20are%20sneered%20at%20for%20ministers%20expressing%20their%20own%20views%2C%20contrary%20to%20that%20held%20by%20governments.%20This%20tells%20its%20own%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDoes%20this%20government%20believe%20in%20collective%20responsibility%3F%20Or%20not%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArticle%2075(3)%20of%20the%20Indian%20Constitution%20spells%20out%20collective%20responsibility%20in%20clear%20and%20uncertain%20terms.%20The%20clause%20reads%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Council%20of%20Ministers%20shall%20be%20collectively%20responsible%20to%20the%20House%20of%20the%20People%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWas%20Lekhi%20responding%20to%20the%20political%20embarrassment%20of%20publicly%20saying%20Hamas%20is%20not%20a%20terrorist%20group%20when%20her%20party%20and%20even%20the%20government%20has%20gone%20out%20of%20its%20way%20to%20support%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20war%20on%20Gaza%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20Palestine%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%20earlier%20today%20(December%2010)%2C%20Modi%2C%20anxious%20to%20keep%20up%20a%20sense%20of%20a%20special%20relationship%20with%20Israel%2C%20and%20especially%20his%20discredited%20counterpart%2C%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20is%20increasingly%20coming%20under%20pressure.%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20actions%20on%20Gaza%20and%20thousands%20of%20civilian%20deaths%20have%20led%20to%20a%20sea%20change%20in%20global%20public%20opinion%20on%20unilaterally%20supporting%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20been%20urging%20India%20to%20ban%20Hamas.%20Recently%2C%20its%20ambassador%20Naor%20Gilon%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fisrael-asks-india-to-declare-hamas-as-a-terrorist-organisation%5C%22%3Ehad%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20with%20Israel%20banning%20terrorist%20organisation%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%2C%20which%20it%20did%2015%20years%20after%20the%20attacks%20in%20Mumbai%2C%20India%20should%20also%20designate%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terror%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20taken%20an%20ambiguous%20stand%20with%20regard%20to%20Hamas%20over%20the%20years%20and%20it%20is%20not%20designated%20a%20terrorist%20group.%20Something%20that%20the%20reply%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20has%20also%20outlined.%20It%20has%20cited%20the%20UN%20as%20a%20guide%2C%20proscribing%20organisations%20that%20have%20officially%20been%20declared%20a%20terrorist%20organisation%20by%20the%20international%20body%2C%20which%20does%20not%20designate%20Hamas%20as%20a%20terrorist%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20despite%20the%20%E2%80%9Creflexive%20Hindutva%20embrace%20of%20Zionism%E2%80%9D%20about%20which%20much%20has%20been%20visible%20in%20the%20public%20for%20a%20while%20and%20documented%2C%20it%20has%20become%20difficult%20for%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20ban%20Hamas%2C%20even%20if%20they%20want%20to%2C%20without%20seriously%20jeopardising%20other%20important%20economic%20and%20strategic%20interests%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20this%20government%20has%20in%20West%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%2C%20for%20designated%20UAPA%20courts%20to%20uphold%20a%20ban%20on%20Hamas%2C%20were%20it%20to%20be%20banned%20domestically%2C%20India%20would%20have%20to%20share%20evidence%20of%20involvement%20of%20the%20organisation%20in%20terror%20activities%20within%20India.%20So%20far%2C%20there%20is%20nothing%20to%20go%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702204259000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F10152334%2Fimage-1589.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-meenakshi-lekhis-public-meltdown-over-hamas-tells-us-about-the-modi-government%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20official%20view%20and%20Lekhi%E2%80%99s%20subsequent%20actions%20raise%20questions%20about%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20about%20how%20decisions%20are%20made%20and%20what%20its%20own%20ministers%20think%20about%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fwhat-meenakshi-lekhis-public-meltdown-over-hamas-tells-us-about-the-modi-government%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Actors%20who%20lost%20weight%20drastically%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702204200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105877558%2Cimgsize-206102.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fweb-series%2Fnews%2Fkorean%2Fpark-min-young-park-seo-joon-lee-min-ki-actors-who-underwent-drastic-weight-loss-transformations%2Fphotostory%2F105877558.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F