the%20incident%2C%20she%20reportedly%20told%20the%20police%20that%20she%20believed%20she%20was%20being%20trafficked%20and%20had%20been%20asked%20to%20engage%20in%20sexual%20acts%20for%20money%2C%20which%20she%20refused.%20However%2C%20she%20admitted%20to%20pouring%20gasoline%20into%20the%20man's%20car%20and%20setting%20it%20on%20fire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2025%2C%20Johnson%20was%20arrested%20following%20allegations%20by%20the%20police%20that%20she%2C%20in%20a%20fit%20of%20anger%2C%20set%20her%20Tinder%20date%20and%20his%20car%20ablaze%20outside%20a%20Holiday%20Inn%20Express%20%26amp%3B%20Suites%20hotel%20in%20Kendall%2C%20Fla.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20man%20told%20the%20police%20that%20Johnson%20approached%20the%20car%20with%20a%201-gallon%20Zephyrhills%20jug%20with%20a%20yellow%20liquid%20in%20it.%20He%20further%20told%20police%20that%20she%20leaned%20in%20to%20talk%20to%20him%2C%20and%20claimed%20that%20she%20asked%20for%20money%20to%20fix%20her%20vehicle.%20He%20responded%20that%20he%20did%20not%20appreciate%20having%20been%20invited%20out%20for%20money%2C%20but%20he%20gave%20her%20%2460%20to%20help%20her%20out%2C%20he%20told%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20revealed%20that%20her%20mood%20changed%20and%20she%20yelled%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20guys%20are%20out%20to%20get%20me!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20then%20poured%20the%20jug%20into%20the%20passenger%20seat%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20when%20he%20tried%20to%20push%20it%20out%2C%20he%20doused%20himself%20and%20Johnson%20in%20the%20liquid%20as%20she%20took%20out%20a%20lighter%20and%20set%20it%20ablaze%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20recounted%20that%20he%20rolled%20onto%20the%20ground%20to%20quell%20the%20flames%2C%20retrieving%20a%20gun%20from%20his%20waistband%20and%20aiming%20it%20at%20her%20in%20case%20she%20tried%20to%20set%20him%20on%20fire%20again%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfterwards%2C%20Johnson%20fled%20t