ia-alliances-next-meeting-in-10-days-seat-sharing-on-agenda-sources-4650869%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Findia-alliances-next-meeting-in-10-days-seat-sharing-on-agenda-sources-4650869%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suryakumar's%20Honest%20Take%20On%20Replacing%20Injured%20Hardik%20As%20T20I%20Skipper%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESouth%20Africa%20will%20pose%20a%20steep%20challenge%20to%20the%20young%20Indian%20side%20in%20the%20T20I%20series%2C%20but%20captain%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20the%20thought%20of%20producing%20a%20stellar%20effort%20out%20of%20their%20%26quot%3Bcomfort%20zone%26quot%3B%20should%20work%20as%20a%20motivation%20for%20the%20players.%20India%20will%20face%20the%20Proteas%20in%20the%20first%20T20I%20of%20the%20three-match%20series%20here%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20go%20outside%20India%2C%20you're%20always%20out%20of%20your%20comfort%20zone%20and%20when%20you%20do%20really%20well%20out%20of%20your%20comfort%20zone%2C%20it%20makes%20a%20lot%20of%20noise%20and%20that%20really%20encourages%20the%20boys.%20So%2C%20really%20looking%20forward%20to%20the%20series%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Suryakumar%20during%20his%20pre-match%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20backed%20his%20fledgling%20squad%20to%20show%20character%20in%20the%20face%20of%20a%20daunting%20opposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20guys%20whom%20I%20am%20watching%20right%20now%20in%20the%20T20s%20are%20very%20expressive%2C%20very%20fearless.%20I%20have%20that%20attitude.%20They%20aren't%20afraid%20of%20failure.%20Whatever%20happens%20if%20they%20do%20good%20or%20if%20they%20don't%20get%20runs%20on%20that%20given%20day%2C%20their%20attitude%20remains%20the%20same.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20balance%20is%20really%20important%20and%20I%20have%20just%20told%20them%20just%20enjoy%20this%20format%2C%20just%20be%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Suryakumar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20gave%20the%20examples%20of%20Rinku%20Singh%20and%20Jitesh%20Sharma%2C%20who%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20the%20home%20series%20win%20against%20Australia%2C%20to%20underscore%20his%20point%20about%20the%20young%20cricketers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRinku%20and%20Jitesh%20so%20far%20have%20the%20opportunity%20to%20bat%20in%20the%20same%20slot%20(for%20India)%20as%20their%20state%20or%20IPL%20teams.%20I%20have%20told%20them%20to%20do%20what%20they%20have%20been%20doing%20for%20those%20teams.%20They%20did%20exactly%20that%20(against%20Australia)%2C%20showing%20some%20character%20in%20some%20tough%20situations%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20noted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bounce%20and%20pace%20on%20South%20African%20pitches%20will%20certainly%20test%20this%20group%20of%20young%20cricketers%2C%20and%20the%20captain%20said%20his%20wards%20are%20well-equipped%20to%20ace%20that%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20key%20to%20success%20to%20playing%20on%20such%20wickets%20will%20be%20to%20be%20yourself.%20We've%20played%20on%20all%20fast%20tracks%20in%20India%20and%20everyone%20is%20really%20equipped%20for%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnd%20regarding%20the%20strokes%20for%20the%20batsmen%2C%20they've%20already%20battered%20on%20these%20kinds%20of%20wickets%20and%20I'm%20sure%20they%20will%20enjoy%20playing%20in%20South%20Africa%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20have%20a%20mere%20six%20more%20T20Is%20ahead%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%2C%20but%20Suryakumar%20down%20played%20the%20minimal%20number%20factor.'%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20only%20limited%20T20s%20before%20the%20T20%20WC.%20But%20then%20we%20play%2014%20league%20games%20in%20the%20IPL%20and%20players%20have%20already%20played%20a%20lot%20of%20games%20and%20they%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20experience%20under%20their%20belt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20I%20don't%20think%20there'll%20be%20an%20issue%20when%20selecting%20the%20squad%20(for%20WC)%20because%20everyone%20knows%20their%20role%20really%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20has%20been%20elevated%20as%20India%20T20I%20captain%20after%20Hardik%20Pandya's%20injury%2C%20and%20the%20Mumbai%20cricketer%20said%20he%20has%20been%20enjoying%20the%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20personal%20point%20of%20view%2C%20it%20(captaincy)%20is%20a%20big%20responsibility.%20I%20really%20enjoyed%20it%20in%20the%20last%20series%20(against%20Australia).%20I%20would%20love%20to%20do%20the%20same%20(winning)%20in%20the%20coming%20series%20in%20South%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20the%20larger%20perspective%2C%20I%20feel%20we'll%20see%20what%20comes%20ahead%20but%20for%20now%20let's%20focus%20on%20the%20series.%26quot%3B%20The%2033-year-old%20admitted%20that%20the%20one-day%20World%20Cup%20final%20defeat%20against%20Australia%20was%20a%20heartbreaking%20one%20but%20the%20series%20win%20against%20the%20same%20opposition%2C%20albeit%2C%20in%20a%20different%20format%2C%20was%20a%20morale%20booster%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20disappointment%20(WC%20final%20defeat)%2C%20which%20will%20be%20difficult%20to%20move%20on%20from.%20But%20as%20I%20always%20say%20the%20show%20must%20go%20on.%20But%20after%20that%20there%20was%20a%20nice%20T20%20series%20against%20Australia.%20We%20really%20enjoyed%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20a%20different%20format.%20It%20(the%20series%20win)%20was%20a%20big%20boost%20for%20the%20boys%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20signed%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702198320000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fkm04p2fo_suryakumar-yadav_625x300_10_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%