e%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scope%20first%20detects%20the%20target%20and%20makes%20a%20red%20bounding%20box%2C%20after%20which%20the%20camera%20checks%20for%20alignment%20using%20the%20laser%20and%20finder%2C%20said%20the%20officer.%20Once%20the%20target%20box%20turns%20green%2C%20the%20shooter%20is%20alerted%20that%20he%20can%20fire%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20scope%20currently%20has%20only%20day%20firing%20capability%2C%20but%20it%20can%20be%20turned%20into%20night%20firing%20device%20too.%20The%20day%20camera%20has%2050mm%20lens%20and%2030X%20zoom.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702195080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-12%2Fn7t3rtsg_smart-scope_625x300_10_December_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-tests-ai-enabled-gun-mounted-scope-says-can-turn-soldier-into-marksman-4650779%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20Army%20is%20testing%20a%20smart%20scope%20powered%20by%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20that%20can%20detect%20humans%20up%20to%20300%20metres%2C%20which%20can%20extensively%20boost%20border%20and%20close%20combat%20operations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-tests-ai-enabled-gun-mounted-scope-says-can-turn-soldier-into-marksman-4650779%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-tests-ai-enabled-gun-mounted-scope-says-can-turn-soldier-into-marksman-4650779%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Farmy-tests-ai-enabled-gun-mounted-scope-says-can-turn-soldier-into-marksman-4650779%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Durban%20is%20an%20ideal%20venue%20for%20India%20to%20start%20SA%20tour%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702194399000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-105876236%2Cimgsize-147558.cms%22%2C%