20R%2FO%20Bemina%20at%20Hamdaniya%20colony%20Bemina.%20He%20has%20been%20shifted%20to%20hospital%20for%20treatment.%20Area%20cordoned%20off.%20Further%20details%20shall%20follow.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20said%20that%20the%20victim%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Karnah%20in%20north%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Kupwara%20district%20who%20was%20presently%20living%20in%20Srinagar%2C%20was%20shifted%20to%20the%20nearby%20SKIMS%20Medical%20College%20in%20Bemina.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20patient%20was%20shifted%20to%20the%20Army%E2%80%99s%20base%20hospital%20after%20initial%20examination%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dr%20Shifa%20A.%20Deva%2C%20Medical%20Superintendent%20of%20SKIMS%20Medical%20College%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20filmed%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20attack%20shows%20a%20group%20of%20gun-toting%20police%20and%20army%20personnel%20arriving%20at%20the%20site%20where%20the%20police%20constable%20was%20shot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBemina%20area%2C%20which%20falls%20on%20Srinagar-Baramulla%20highway%2C%20has%20a%20history%20of%20attacks%20on%20security%20personnel.%20In%202021%2C%20a%20police%20constable%20was%20shot%20and%20killed%20in%20a%20militant%20attack.%20In%202013%2C%20five%20security%20personnel%20were%20killed%20while%20ten%20more%20were%20injured%20in%20a%20suicide%20attack%20which%20was%20claimed%20by%20Hizbul%20Mujahideen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20recent%20attack%20took%20place%20a%20day%20after%20a%20J%26amp%3BK%20police%20inspector%2C%20who%20was%20injured%20in%20a%20militant%20attack%20on%20October%2029%20this%20year%2C%20succumbed%20to%20his%20injuries%20at%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Science%20in%20New%20Delhi.%20The%20victim%2C%20Masroor%20Ahmad%20Wani%2C%20was%20airlifted%20to%20the%20national%20capital%20earlier%20this%20week%20after%20his%20condition%20deteriorated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20reporters%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20wreath%20laying%20ceremony%20for%20the%20slain%20inspector%2C%20Additional%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20(Law%20and%20Order)%20Vijay%20Kumar%20had%20asserted%20that%20the%20officers%20and%20other%20ranks%20of%20police%20have%20been%20directed%20to%20follow%20Standard%20Operating%20Procedure%20to%20avoid%20incidents%20like%20the%20one%20in%20which%20Wani%20was%20targeted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20off-duty%20cop%20was%20shot%20and%20critically%20injured%20while%20playing%20cricket%20at%20Eidgah%20ground%20in%20Srinagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20while%20speaking%20in%20the%20parliament%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fbefore-celebrating-a-fall-in-jk-terror-amit-shah-would-do-well-to-look-deeper-into-the-numbers%5C%22%3Esaid%20that%20the%20incidents%20of%20terrorism%20have%20reduced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20following%20the%20reading%20down%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20bifurcation%20of%20the%20erstwhile%20state%20into%20two%20union%20territories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20official%20data%20suggests%20that%20Jammu%20region%2C%20which%20was%20largely%20militancy-free%20before%20J%26amp%3BK%20lost%20its%20special%20constitutional%20position%2C%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fbefore-celebrating-a-fall-in-jk-terror-amit-shah-would-do-well-to-look-deeper-into-the-numbers%5C%22%3Ewitnessed%20a%20sharp%20rise%20in%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20civilians%20and%20security%20forces%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20last%20two%20years%20during%20which%20more%20than%20two%20dozen%20security%20personnel%20were%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702138628000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F07172741%2FJK-police.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsecurity%2Fjk-police-officer-shot-by-suspected-militants-on-outskirts-of-srinagar%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20senior%20police%20