rritated%20in%20my%20case.%20I%20am%20a%20grown-up%20who%20is%20capable%20of%20making%20decisions.%20When%20I%20could%20not%20continue%20the%20marriage%20(with%20Jahan)%2C%20I%20got%20out%20of%20it.%20Now%2C%20I%20have%20married%20another%20person%20of%20my%20choice.%20I%20am%20happy%20and%20living%20as%20a%20Muslim.%20My%20parents%20are%20also%20aware%20about%20the%20remarriage%E2%80%9D%20she%20said%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20was%20released%20a%20day%20after%20her%20father%20K.M.%20Ashokan%20moved%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20petition%20in%20the%20Kerala%20high%20court%20alleging%20that%20he%20could%20not%20reach%20Hadiya%20over%20the%20phone%20and%20her%20homeopathy%20clinic%20was%20shut.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Hadiya%20said%20on%20Saturday%20that%20she%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20know%20why%20her%20father%20moved%20the%20high%20court.%20She%20did%20not%20disclose%20details%20of%20her%20new%20partner%2C%20saying%20there%20was%20no%20need%20to%20make%20them%20public.%20She%20has%20moved%20to%20Thiruvananthapuram%20from%20Mallapuram%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EIndian%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fhadiyas-father-moves-court-again-this-time-alleging-illegal-detention-101702061000388.html%5C%22%3EAccording%20to%20%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20said%20her%20%E2%80%9Cfather%20has%20created%20troubles%20making%20it%20difficult%20for%20me%20to%20live.%20There%20have%20been%20cyberattacks%20on%20me%20which%20has%20made%20my%20life%20difficult.%20My%20father%20has%20always%20been%20made%20a%20tool%20by%20the%20Sangh%20Parivar%20forces.%20It%20is%20sad%20that%20he%20is%20allowing%20himself%20to%20be%20used%20that%20way.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHadiya%20also%20denied%20the%20claims%20that%20her%20phone%20was%20switched%20off%2C%20stating%20instead%20that%20she%20was%20%E2%80%9Cin%20constant%20touch%20with%20her%20parents%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CI%20have%20remarried%20and%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20think%20it%20needs%20to%20be%20a%20subject%20of%20discussion%20again.%20I%20am%20a%20mature%20adult%20who%20is%20capable%20of%20taking%20her%20own%20decisions%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20into%20a%20Hindu%20family%20in%20Kottayam%2C%20Hadiya%20said%20she%20was%20drawn%20to%20Islam%20when%20studying%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20She%20converted%20to%20that%20faith%20and%20married%20Jahan.%20Her%20father%20filed%20a%20habeas%20corpus%20plea%20in%202016%2C%20challenging%20the%20marriage.%20The%20high%20court%20nullified%20the%20marriage%20and%20ordered%20her%20to%20be%20placed%20in%20the%20protective%20custody%20of%20her%20Hindu%20parents%20or%20an%20institution%2C%20so%20that%20she%20is%20%E2%80%9Cprevented%20from%20being%20a%20further%20victim%20of%20%3Cem%3Elove%20jihad%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D.%20The%20judgment%20was%20perhaps%20the%20first%20time%20that%20a%20constitutional%20court%20used%20this%20term%2C%20a%20conspiracy%20theory%20that%20claims%20there%20is%20a%20plot%20to%20convert%20Hindu%20women%20to%20Islam%20through%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20in%20March%202018%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-sets-aside-kerala-hc-order-annulling-hadiya-marriage%5C%22%3Erestored%3C%2Fa%3E%20her%20marriage%20and%20allowed%20her%20to%20live%20with%20her%20husband%20Jahan.%C2%A0The%20top%20court%20allowed%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20to%20probe%20the%20incident%20to%20see%20if%20she%20was%20forced%20to%20convert%20to%20Islam.%20The%20agency%20later%20closed%20the%20case%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnia-love-jihad-kerala-hadiya%5C%22%3Efinding%20no%20evidence%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20support%20such%20a%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702108801000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2