d%20multiple%20job%20offers%2C%20are%20struggling%20to%20get%20even%20a%20single%20offer.%20%E2%80%9CRecruiters%20who%20used%20to%20hire%208-10%20students%20are%20now%20taking%201-2%20students%20each%3B%20some%20are%20coming%20to%20campus%20but%20leaving%20without%20recruiting%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20student%20at%20IIT-Kharagpur%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20gloomy%20scenario%20is%20attributable%20to%20the%20slowdown%20being%20witnessed%20across%20multiple%20sectors%2C%20including%20tech%2C%20consulting%2C%20and%20other%20services%20sectors.%20Economic%20shifts%2C%20geopolitical%20economic%20worries%2C%20and%20recession%20fears%20have%20resulted%20in%20the%20slowdown%20globally.%20The%20current%20slowdown%2C%20which%20is%20being%20witnessed%20specifically%20in%20the%20information%20technology%20(IT)%20sector%2C%20is%20expected%20to%20drag%20on%20for%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20quarters%2C%20Sekhar%20Garisa%2C%20CEO%20of%20job%20portal%20Foundit%20(formerly%20Monster)%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Fit-hiring-slowdown-to-continue-for-2-3-quarters-global-slowdown-to-blame-123112900556_1.html%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%20%3Cem%3EFinancial%20Express%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20tide%20over%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%2C%20%E2%80%9Cnon-tech%20sectors%20such%20as%20automobile%2C%20retail%2C%20and%20banking%20will%20be%20the%20saviours%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20tech%20talent%20as%20the%20traditional%20haven%20IT%20sector%20reduces%20hiring%20significantly%E2%80%9D%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20Businessline%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Finfo-tech%2Ftech-talent-finds-new-haven-in-non-tech-sectors-amid-it-hiring-slowdown%2Farticle67462067.ece%5C%22%3Ehad%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20situation%20is%20also%20concerning%20at%20older%20IITs%20of%20Delhi%2C%20Bombay%2C%20Kanpur%2C%20Madras%2C%20Kharagpur%2C%20Roorkee%2C%20Guwahati%20and%20Varanasi%20(BHU).%20Of%20the%20total%2023%20IITs%20in%20the%20country%2C%20the%20older%20IITs%20are%20more%20prestigious%20than%20others%2C%20and%20it%20is%20extremely%20competitive%20to%20secure%20a%20seat%20in%20one%20of%20these%20institutes.%20As%20they%20attract%20the%20%3Cem%3Ecr%C3%A8me%20de%20la%20cr%C3%A8me%3C%2Fem%3E%20of%20the%20student%20lot%2C%20recruiters%20vie%20with%20each%20other%20to%20provide%20job%20offers%20to%20these%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20vicious%20cycle.%20Earlier%20when%20there%20was%20a%20rush%2C%20everyone%20used%20to%20compete%20to%20hire%20students.%20Now%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20slowdown%2C%20others%20are%20also%20questioning%20whether%20they%20need%20as%20many%20students%20as%20they%20had%20hired%20in%20the%20past%2C%E2%80%9D%20another%20student%20told%20%3Cem%3EET%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIIT-Kharagpur%20received%201%2C181%20offers%20as%20of%20day%20seven%20of%20the%20placement%20drive%3B%20the%20number%20is%20significantly%20lower%20compared%20to%20the%201%2C300%20offers%20the%20institute%20had%20received%20by%20the%20end%20of%20day%20five%20last%20year.%20Similarly%2C%20IIT-BHU%20has%20so%20far%20received%20850%20offers%20while%20it%20was%201%2C000%20offers%20within%20four%20days%20of%20the%20placement%20drive%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1702108260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F09130925%2FEffect-21.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Feconomic-slowdown-affects-placements-at-iits-hiring-declines-by-15-to-30-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Even%20after%20a%20week%20of%20the%20placement%20drive%20has%20passed%2C%20most%20students%20are%20yet%20to%20land%20a%20job%2C%20and%20the%20situation%20ahead%20looks%20bleak.%C2%A0%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fl